author: Pradeep Gupta
title: Chief minister Devendra Fadnavis dances to Narendra Modi’s tune: Raj Thackeray
text:
KALYAN: MNS chief Raj Thackeray on Friday targeted chief minister Devendra Fadvanis saying he dances to the tune of Prime Minister Narendra Modi. Thackeray was addressing party workers in Kalyan, while campaigning for the KDMC polls. He said that before taking any decision, Fadnavis waits for orders from Modi as he cannot make any decision by himself. Targeting Modi, the MNS chief asked where are the "Acchey din" he had promised.
Thackeray also accused the BJP of "purchasing" candidates from other parties to win polls
